-bash: warning: setlocale: LC_CTYPE: cannot change locale (UTF-8): 没有那个文件或目录


LANG="zh_CN.UTF-8"


su 和 su - 的区别


安装完mysql（yum方式安装）执行命令 ’ mysql ‘报错：
	ERROR 2002 (HY000): Can't connect to local MySQL server through socket '/var/lib/mysql/mysql.sock' (2)


> 使用mysql过程中报错:  Data source rejected establishment of connection, message from server: "Too many connections"
 -- 解决： 修改mysql的连接数
 	# 查看当前设置的最大连接数
 	$ select VARIABLE_VALUE from information_schema.GLOBAL_VARIABLES where VARIABLE_NAME='MAX_CONNECTIONS'; 

 	#  修改最大连接数
 	$ set global max_connections = 3600;	# 临时修改，重启mysql服务即失效


> 登录linux报错
	bash: warning: setlocale: LC_CTYPE: cannot change locale (UTF-8): No such file or directory
	-bash: warning: setlocale: LC_COLLATE: cannot change locale (cn_CH.UTF-8): No such file or directory
	-bash: warning: setlocale: LC_MESSAGES: cannot change locale (cn_CH.UTF-8): No such file or directory
	-bash: warning: setlocale: LC_NUMERIC: cannot change locale (cn_CH.UTF-8): No such file or directory
	-bash: warning: setlocale: LC_TIME: cannot change locale (cn_CH.UTF-8): No such file or directory

	执行locale查看错误所在
	修改错误
		vim  /etc/sysconfig/i18n   # 编辑文件
		LANG="en_US.UTF-8"  	# 注意大小写
		source /etc/sysconfig/i18n	#  使修改生效